step 1:
- Signup -
method POST: https://messages-app-abra.herokuapp.com/signup
body > form-data
username: abra
password: 123456

step 2:
- Login -
method POST: https://messages-app-abra.herokuapp.com/login
body > form-data
username: abra
password: 123456

step 3:
- Write message -
method POST: https://messages-app-abra.herokuapp.com/messages
body > form-data
receiver: 1
subject: Hi
message: hello word

step 4:
- Get all messages for a specific user -
method GET https://messages-app-abra.herokuapp.com/messages

step 5:
- Get all unread messages for a specific user -
method GET: https://messages-app-abra.herokuapp.com/messages?unread

step 6:
- Read message (return one message) -
method GET: https://messages-app-abra.herokuapp.com/messages/<input_message_id>
* example *
method Get: https://messages-app-abra.herokuapp.com/messages/4


step 6:
- Delete message (as owner or as receiver) -
method DELETE: https://messages-app-abra.herokuapp.com/messages/<input_message_id>